default&#xa0;defaultDeclaration of interests.defaultWienerberger
default AG is the world’s largest producer of clay bricks and number 1 in clay roof tiles in Europe with 230 factories in 30 countries. Most of these are situated in EU Member States but some are outside the EU including the USA and India. The Group Head Office is based in Vienna.
