default Ltd in the UK – including the sister Company 
defaultSandtoft
default Roof Tiles Ltd – have a total of 14 manufacturing sites and a current workforce of around 1,000. Only 13 of these sites are currently operational.
default The Company manufactures clay facing and engineering bricks, clay pavers and roof tiles manufactured in clay, concrete and reconstituted slate.
